        <abstract>
            <p>Asks for a photograph of CL to be used by a society [in Serbia].</p> 
<p>Comments on article by Wallace ["Sir Charles Lyell on geological climates and the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>", <hi rend="italic">Q. Rev.</hi> 126 (1869): 359–94].</p>  
<p>Has finished new edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [5th (1869)]</p>  
<p>and is back at work on sexual selection [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>].</p> 
        </abstract>
